# <type>(<module>/<layer>): <short summary>
#
# Examples:
#   feat(master-data/application): add MAT101 fund center search
#   fix(master-data/infrastructure): prevent duplicate migrations
#   refactor(shared/kernel): standardize domain exceptions
#   test(master-data/domain): add validation coverage
#   docs: update API naming conventions
#
# Types:
#   feat      = new feature
#   fix       = bug fix
#   refactor  = internal code change, no behavior change
#   test      = add or update tests
#   docs      = documentation only
#   chore     = tooling, config, deps
#   style     = formatting, naming, linting
#   perf      = performance improvement
#   ci        = CI/CD related
#   hotfix    = urgent production fix
#
# Scope guidelines:
#   module    = master-data | hr | key | fram | shared | api | infra
#   layer     = domain | application | infrastructure | api | kernel
#
# Body (optional):
#   - What changed?
#   - Why is this change needed?
#   - Any important side effects?
#
# Footer (optional):
#   - Breaking changes
#   - Related ticket / issue ID
#
